@baseUrl = http://localhost:5173
@apiPath = /api/transactions


### 1. Valid seat number — expect 200 with student info + transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?seat=X039423
Accept: application/json


### 2. Another seat number
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?seat=B202
Accept: application/json


### 3. Missing seat param — expect 400
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}
Accept: application/json


### 4. Seat not found in DB — expect 404
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?seat=XXXX999
Accept: application/json


### 5. Seat with special characters (edge case)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?seat=A-101
Accept: application/json


### 6. Empty seat param — expect 400
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?seat=
Accept: application/json



### SSC seat — recheck_type 1 (without photocopy) — all subjects
GET http://localhost:5173/api/check_inserted?seat=H081576&recheck_type=1&subjects=MARATHI (1ST LANG),HINDI (2/3 LANG),ENGLISH (2/3 LANG),MATHEMATICS,SOCIAL SCIENCES,SCIENCE & TECHNOLOGY

